<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="get-the-message">get the message</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>[非正式用语] 领悟；理解；明白 (别人的暗示)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Mark, I think you’re the right person for the job.
马克，我认为你是这个职位的合适人选。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— I get the message. 
我明白了。</p></div></div>